---

<Layout title="Dolphin House Beach Resort Rooms & Prices | Official Site | Nagaon Alibaug" 
description="Official rooms and prices page for Dolphin House Beach Resort in Nagaon, Alibaug. Compare AC, deluxe, and family room rates, reviews, and direct booking options near Nagaon Beach." 
image="/uploader/room-9.webp" ogType="hotel" faqSchema={faqSchema}>

  <section class="relative mb-16">
    <img
      src="/uploader/hotel-front-1.webp"
      srcset="/uploader/hotel-front-1-480x320.webp 480w, /uploader/hotel-front-1-960x640.webp 960w, /uploader/hotel-front-1.webp 1267w"
      sizes="(min-width: 1024px) 1267px, (min-width: 768px) 960px, 100vw"
      alt="Rooms in Nagaon Alibaug near beach at Dolphin House resort"
      class="w-full h-80 md:h-[450px] object-cover rounded-3xl shadow-xl"
      width="1267" height="1067" decoding="async" fetchpriority="high" />
    <div class="absolute inset-0 bg-black/50 flex items-center justify-center rounded-3xl">
      <h1 class="text-4xl md:text-6xl font-extrabold text-white text-center tracking-tight px-4">
        Dolphin House Beach Resort Rooms & Prices in Nagaon Alibaug
      </h1>
    </div>
  </section>

  <p class="text-lg font-semibold text-yellow-500 mt-3 text-center">
⭐ Rated 4.1/5 • 2 min walk to beach • Best direct prices
</p>

  <section class="text-center mb-16 max-w-4xl mx-auto">
    <h2 class="text-3xl font-bold text-gray-800 mb-4">Relax in Comfort by the Beach</h2>
    <p class="text-lg text-gray-600 leading-relaxed">
      Looking for rooms in Nagaon Alibaug near the beach? Dolphin House offers AC and non-AC rooms, family rooms, and deluxe cottages just 2 minutes from Nagaon Beach. Ideal for couples, families, and groups, our rooms provide comfort, affordability, and easy beach access for a perfect Alibaug stay.
    </p>
    <p class="text-base text-gray-600 text-center mt-4">
    📍 Looking for Dolphin House? We are located in Nagaon, Alibaug (Maharashtra) — the perfect weekend getaway from Mumbai and Pune. We are not affiliated with properties in Goa or the Philippines.
    </p>
    <div class="mt-6 flex flex-wrap justify-center gap-3">
      <a href="/booking" class="rounded-full border border-sky-200 bg-sky-50 px-5 py-3 font-semibold text-sky-700 transition hover:border-sky-400 hover:bg-sky-100">
        Check Direct Booking
      </a>
      <a href="https://www.google.com/search?q=Dolphin+House+Beach+Resort+Reviews" target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer" class="rounded-full border border-amber-200 bg-amber-50 px-5 py-3 font-semibold text-amber-900 transition hover:border-amber-400 hover:bg-amber-100">
        Read Reviews
      </a>
      <a href="/gallery" class="rounded-full border border-emerald-200 bg-emerald-50 px-5 py-3 font-semibold text-emerald-800 transition hover:border-emerald-400 hover:bg-emerald-100">
        View Room Photos
      </a>
    </div>
    <p class="text-base text-gray-600 leading-relaxed mt-4">
      If you are comparing a <a href="/beach-resort-in-nagaon-alibaug" class="font-semibold text-sky-600 hover:underline">beach resort in Nagaon Alibaug</a> with room-only options, Dolphin House gives you both location convenience and a full resort experience close to the shoreline.
    </p>
    <p class="text-base text-gray-600 leading-relaxed mt-3">
      Guests who want a <a href="/resort-with-swimming-pool-alibaug" class="font-semibold text-sky-600 hover:underline">resort with swimming pool in Alibaug</a> can also enjoy our indoor pool, beach proximity, and family-friendly stay setup in one place.
    </p>
    <p class="text-base text-gray-600 leading-relaxed mt-3">
      Still comparing stay types? Explore our guides for a
      <a href="/resort-in-alibaug" class="font-semibold text-sky-600 hover:underline">resort in Alibaug</a>,
      <a href="/beach-resort-alibaug" class="font-semibold text-sky-600 hover:underline">beach resort in Alibaug</a>, and
      <a href="/nagaon-beach-resort" class="font-semibold text-sky-600 hover:underline">Nagaon Beach resort</a>
      before choosing the best room category.
    </p>
    <p class="text-base text-gray-600 leading-relaxed mt-3">
      Traveling with children or a larger group? Read our
      <a href="/alibaug-family-group-guide-2026" class="font-semibold text-sky-600 hover:underline">2026 Alibaug family and group guide</a>
      to compare beaches, activities, and the best stay setup before you book.
    </p>
    <p class="text-base text-gray-600 leading-relaxed mt-3">
      Still deciding between Nagaon and Alibaug town? Our
      <a href="/why-smart-travelers-choose-nagaon" class="font-semibold text-sky-600 hover:underline">location comparison guide</a>
      explains why repeat visitors often prefer staying here in Nagaon.
    </p>
    <p class="text-base text-gray-600 leading-relaxed mt-3">
      <a href="/group-corporate-bookings" class="font-semibold text-sky-600 hover:underline">Planning a group trip? Check our Group Packages.</a>
      This page covers family reunions, corporate offsites, group dining, and discounted rates for multi-room stays.
    </p>
  </section>

  <section class="text-center max-w-3xl mx-auto mt-6">
    <h2 class="text-2xl font-bold">
      Book Rooms in Alibaug Near Nagaon Beach
    </h2>

    <p class="text-gray-600 mt-3">
      Looking for room booking in Alibaug near beach? Dolphin House offers AC and non-AC rooms, 
      family rooms, and budget-friendly options just 2 minutes from Nagaon Beach.
    </p>

    <p class="text-gray-600 mt-3">
      Compare room prices, occupancy, and facilities to choose the best stay for your trip.
    </p>
  </section>

  <section class="mb-14 max-w-5xl mx-auto rounded-3xl border border-cyan-100 bg-cyan-50 p-8 text-center">
    <h2 class="text-3xl font-bold text-cyan-950 mb-4">Looking for Dolphin House Beach Resort prices or reviews?</h2>
    <p class="text-lg text-gray-700 leading-relaxed">
      Guests often search for <strong>Dolphin House Beach Resort prices</strong>, <strong>Dolphin House Beach Resort reviews</strong>, and the <strong>official website</strong> before booking. This page is the official room and tariff page for Dolphin House Beach Resort in Nagaon, Alibaug.
    </p>
    <p class="mt-4 text-base text-gray-700 leading-relaxed">
      Current room tariffs on this page start from <strong>Rs. 2900</strong>, and you can compare room size, guest capacity, and AC options before contacting us for direct booking.
    </p>
  </section>

  <section class="mb-14 max-w-5xl mx-auto rounded-3xl border border-amber-100 bg-amber-50 p-8 text-center">
    <h2 class="text-3xl font-bold text-amber-950 mb-4">Which Room is Right for You?</h2>
    <div class="grid gap-4 md:grid-cols-3 text-left">
      <div class="rounded-2xl bg-white p-5 shadow-sm ring-1 ring-amber-100">
        <h3 class="text-xl font-semibold text-gray-900 mb-2">Couples</h3>
        <p class="text-gray-700">Standard Room or Deluxe Room</p>
      </div>
      <div class="rounded-2xl bg-white p-5 shadow-sm ring-1 ring-amber-100">
        <h3 class="text-xl font-semibold text-gray-900 mb-2">Small Families (3–4)</h3>
        <p class="text-gray-700">Deluxe Room or Family Room</p>
      </div>
      <div class="rounded-2xl bg-white p-5 shadow-sm ring-1 ring-amber-100">
        <h3 class="text-xl font-semibold text-gray-900 mb-2">Large Families / Groups</h3>
        <p class="text-gray-700">Deluxe Family Room</p>
      </div>
    </div>
    <p class="mt-6 text-base text-gray-700 leading-relaxed">
      All rooms are located near Nagaon Beach and provide easy access to the swimming pool and restaurant.
    </p>
  </section>

  <section class="grid sm:grid-cols-2 lg:grid-cols-3 gap-10">
    {roomCategories.map(room => (
      <div class="group bg-white rounded-2xl shadow-lg overflow-hidden border border-gray-100 hover:shadow-2xl transition transform hover:-translate-y-1">
        <div class="relative overflow-hidden">
          <img
            src={room.image}
            alt={room.alt}
            class="w-full h-64 object-cover group-hover:scale-110 transition duration-500"
            width={room.width} height={room.height} loading="lazy" decoding="async" />
          <div class="absolute top-0 left-0 bg-sky-600 text-white px-3 py-1 text-sm rounded-br-xl shadow-md">
            {room.type}
          </div>
        </div>
        <div class="p-6 flex flex-col justify-between h-[340px]">
          <div>
            <h3 class="text-xl font-bold text-gray-800 mb-2">{room.title}</h3>
            <p class="text-gray-600 text-sm mb-3">{room.description}</p>
            <ul class="text-sm text-gray-500 space-y-1">
              <li>👥 <strong>Max Guests:</strong> {room.max}</li>
              <li>📏 <strong>Size:</strong> {room.area} sq.ft</li>
              <li>💰 <strong>Tariff:</strong> ₹{room.rateNonAC} (Non-AC) / ₹{room.rateAC} (AC)</li>
            </ul>
          </div>
          <div class="mt-4 flex flex-col gap-3">
            <div class="flex justify-between items-center text-xs text-gray-500">
              <span>Max Guests: {room.max}</span>
              <span class="italic">+ ₹700 / extra person</span>
            </div>
            <div class="flex gap-2">
              <a href="/booking" class="flex-1 bg-sky-600 text-white font-semibold py-2 rounded-lg hover:bg-sky-700 transition text-sm shadow-md text-center">
                Book Now
              </a>
              {room.videoUrl && (
                <a href={room.videoUrl} target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer" class="flex-1 border border-sky-600 text-sky-600 font-semibold py-2 rounded-lg hover:bg-sky-50 transition text-sm shadow-sm text-center flex items-center justify-center gap-1">
                  <span>▶</span> 360° Tour
                </a>
              )}
            </div>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
    ))}
  </section>

  <section class="mt-12 max-w-4xl mx-auto rounded-3xl border border-red-100 bg-red-50 p-7 text-center shadow-sm">
    <p class="text-lg text-gray-700 leading-relaxed">
      ⚠️ Weekend rooms at Dolphin House sell out fast – Book early to get best price
    </p>
  </section>

  <section class="mt-20 bg-blue-50/50 border border-blue-100 rounded-3xl p-10 shadow-inner text-center">
    <h2 class="text-3xl font-bold text-gray-800 mb-6">Room Features & Facilities</h2>
    <div class="grid sm:grid-cols-2 md:grid-cols-3 lg:grid-cols-4 gap-6 text-gray-700">
      <div class="feature-card">🛏️ Air-conditioned Rooms</div>
      <div class="feature-card">📺 Satellite TV</div>
      <div class="feature-card">💧 Attached Bathrooms</div>
      <div class="feature-card">🌐 Free Wi-Fi</div>
      <div class="feature-card">⚡ Generator Backup</div>
      <div class="feature-card">🏊 Indoor Swimming Pool</div>
      <div class="feature-card">🍽️ In-house Restaurant</div>
      <div class="feature-card">🚗 Car Parking</div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <section class="mb-14 max-w-4xl mx-auto overflow-hidden rounded-2xl border border-gray-200 shadow-sm">
  <table class="w-full text-left border-collapse">
    <thead class="bg-gray-100">
      <tr>
        <th class="p-4 font-bold text-gray-800">Feature</th>
        <th class="p-4 font-bold text-gray-800">Dolphin House (Nagaon)</th>
      </tr>
    </thead>
    <tbody class="divide-y divide-gray-200">
      <tr>
        <td class="p-4 text-gray-600">Location</td>
        <td class="p-4 text-gray-900 font-medium">Nagaon, Alibaug, Maharashtra (Not Goa)</td>
      </tr>
      <tr>
        <td class="p-4 text-gray-600">Travel Time</td>
        <td class="p-4 text-gray-900 font-medium">3 Hours from Mumbai / Pune</td>
      </tr>
      <tr>
        <td class="p-4 text-gray-600">Beach Access</td>
        <td class="p-4 text-gray-900 font-medium">150 Meters from Nagaon Beach</td>
      </tr>
    </tbody>
  </table>
</section>

  <section class="mt-20 py-12 bg-white rounded-3xl border border-gray-100 shadow-sm">
    <div class="max-w-4xl mx-auto px-6">
      <h2 class="text-3xl font-bold text-gray-800 mb-8 text-center">Guest Experiences</h2>

      <div class="bg-sky-50 p-8 rounded-2xl relative">
        <span class="absolute top-4 left-4 text-6xl text-sky-200 font-serif">“</span>

        <div class="relative z-10">
          <p class="text-lg text-gray-700 italic leading-relaxed mb-6">
            "The fantastic place to stay-I can't even call it a hotel or a cottage because it seems like home to my family and myself. The meal was fantastic and the services provided by the staff are unmatched. This is very much close to beach, just a 2 mins walking distance."
          </p>

          <div class="flex items-center gap-4">
            <div class="w-12 h-12 bg-sky-600 rounded-full flex items-center justify-center text-white font-bold text-xl">
              R
            </div>
            <div>
              <h4 class="font-bold text-gray-900">Rakesh Rane</h4>
              <div class="flex text-yellow-400 text-sm">
                ★★★★★ <span class="ml-2 text-gray-500 font-normal">Google Review</span>
              </div>
            </div>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>

      <div class="text-center mt-8">
        <a href="https://www.google.com/search?q=Dolphin+House+Beach+Resort+Reviews" target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer" class="text-sky-600 font-semibold hover:underline">
          Read more reviews on Google →
        </a>
      </div>
      <div class="text-center mt-6">
      <p class="text-gray-700 font-medium">
        Stayed with us? Share your experience!
      </p>
        <a href="https://g.page/r/Cdf5KlWcXCsMEBM/review" target="_blank" 
        class="inline-block mt-3 bg-green-600 text-white px-6 py-3 rounded-lg font-semibold hover:bg-green-700 transition">
        ⭐ Write a Google Review
      </a>
    </div>
    </div>
  </section>
  
  <section class="mt-20">
    <div class="max-w-4xl mx-auto text-center mb-8">
      <h2 class="text-3xl font-bold text-gray-800 mb-4">Enjoy a Resort Stay with Swimming Pool in Alibaug</h2>
      <p class="text-lg text-gray-600 leading-relaxed">
        All guests at Dolphin House can access our indoor swimming pool with waterfall. Whether you want to relax after a beach visit or spend quality time with family, our pool adds comfort to your stay.
      </p>
      <p class="text-base text-gray-600 leading-relaxed mt-3">
        Looking specifically for a pool stay? Explore our dedicated page for a
        <a href="/resort-with-swimming-pool-alibaug" class="font-semibold text-sky-600 hover:underline">resort with swimming pool in Alibaug</a>.
      </p>
    </div>
    <div class="grid sm:grid-cols-2 lg:grid-cols-4 gap-6">
      <img
        src="/uploader/swimming-pool1.webp"
        srcset="/uploader/swimming-pool1-480x320.webp 480w, /uploader/swimming-pool1-960x640.webp 960w, /uploader/swimming-pool1.webp 1600w"
        sizes="(min-width: 1024px) 25vw, (min-width: 640px) 50vw, 100vw"
        alt="Indoor swimming pool at Dolphin House resort with swimming pool in Alibaug"
        class="rounded-2xl shadow-md w-full h-56 object-cover hover:scale-105 transition"
        width="1600" height="945" loading="lazy" decoding="async" />
      <img
        src="/uploader/swimming-pool1_1.webp"
        alt="Indoor pool seating area at Dolphin House resort with swimming pool in Alibaug"
        class="rounded-2xl shadow-md w-full h-56 object-cover hover:scale-105 transition"
        width="1600" height="943" loading="lazy" decoding="async" />
      <img
        src="/uploader/swimming-pool2.webp"
        alt="Swimming pool view at Dolphin House stay near beach in Alibaug"
        class="rounded-2xl shadow-md w-full h-56 object-cover hover:scale-105 transition"
        width="1600" height="945" loading="lazy" decoding="async" />
      <img
        src="/uploader/swimming-pool3.webp"
        alt="Indoor swimming pool with waterfall at Dolphin House resort in Nagaon Alibaug"
        class="rounded-2xl shadow-md w-full h-56 object-cover hover:scale-105 transition"
        width="1600" height="943" loading="lazy" decoding="async" />
    </div>
  </section>

  <section class="mt-20 max-w-4xl mx-auto rounded-3xl border border-gray-200 bg-white p-8 shadow-sm">
    <h2 class="text-3xl font-bold text-gray-800 mb-6 text-center">Frequently Asked Questions</h2>
    <div class="space-y-4">
      <details class="group rounded-2xl border border-gray-200 bg-gray-50 p-5">
        <summary class="cursor-pointer list-none text-lg font-semibold text-gray-900 flex items-center justify-between gap-4">
          <span>What is the price of rooms in Nagaon Alibaug?</span>
          <span class="text-sky-600 transition-transform group-open:rotate-45">+</span>
        </summary>
        <p class="mt-3 text-gray-600 leading-relaxed">Room prices at Dolphin House Beach Resort in Nagaon, Alibaug start from Rs. 2900 and vary based on room type and AC option.</p>
      </details>
      <details class="group rounded-2xl border border-gray-200 bg-gray-50 p-5">
        <summary class="cursor-pointer list-none text-lg font-semibold text-gray-900 flex items-center justify-between gap-4">
          <span>How far are the rooms from Nagaon Beach?</span>
          <span class="text-sky-600 transition-transform group-open:rotate-45">+</span>
        </summary>
        <p class="mt-3 text-gray-600 leading-relaxed">All rooms are located just a 2-minute walk from Nagaon Beach.</p>
      </details>
      <details class="group rounded-2xl border border-gray-200 bg-gray-50 p-5">
        <summary class="cursor-pointer list-none text-lg font-semibold text-gray-900 flex items-center justify-between gap-4">
          <span>Do rooms include access to swimming pool?</span>
          <span class="text-sky-600 transition-transform group-open:rotate-45">+</span>
        </summary>
